<item>
            <title>[LU-7664] set_conf_param_and_check() defect : it should wait update on facet_active_host instead of facet_host</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7664</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;set_conf_param_and_check() should wait update on facet_active_host&lt;br/&gt;
instead of facet_host;&lt;br/&gt;
the described defect causes conf-sanity test_27b failure on configuration:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt; mds1_HOST != mds1failover_HOST
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;fre902: error: get_param: /proc/{fs,sys}/{lnet,lustre}/mdt/lustre-MDT0000/identity_acquire_expire: Found no match
pdsh@fre907: fre902: ssh exited with exit code 3
Update not seen after 90s: wanted &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;35&apos;&lt;/span&gt; got &apos;&apos;
 conf-sanity test_27b: @@@@@@ FAIL: check lustre-MDT0000.mdt.identity_acquire_expire failed! 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
